## 10. Work Units

| # | Unit | Dependencies | Est. Complexity |
|---|------|-------------|-----------------|
| 1 | JSON schema + init script | None | Low |
| 2 | Calibration computation (rolling avg, clamping, jq) | 1 | Medium |
| 3a | Behavioral feedback templates | 2 | Medium |
| 3b | Feedback generation logic | 2, 3a | Medium |
| 4 | SessionStart hook (preflight injection) | 1, 2, 3b | Medium |
| 5 | SessionEnd hook (postflight computation) | 1, 2, 3b, 4 | High |
| 6 | CLAUDE.md instruction updates | 3b | Low |
